object.script:
messages={"." } cols={{255,255,255}} col={0,0,0} font_w=4 font_h=5 scroll=0 my_m="" incoming_buffer="" outgoing_buffer="" send=false t=0 recv=false function split(a,b) result={} from=1 delim_from,delim_to=string.find(a,b,from) while delim_from do table.insert(result,string.sub(a,from,delim_from-1)) from=delim_to+1 delim_from,delim_to=string.find(a,b,from) end table.insert(result,string.sub(a,from)) return result end
function onTick() t=t+1 x=input.getNumber(3) y=input.getNumber(4) w=input.getNumber(1) h=input.getNumber(2) pressed=input.getBool(1) if pressed then if x>w-9 and x<w-3 and y<4 then scroll=math.max(scroll-1,0) elseif x>w-9 and x<w-3 and y>h-font_h*3-10 and y<h-(font_h+1)*3 then scroll=scroll+1 end end byte=input.getNumber(8) if byte==8 then my_m=string.sub(my_m,1,#my_m-1) elseif byte>0 then my_m=my_m..string.char(byte) end recv=input.getNumber(13)~=0 for c=13,15 do if input.getNumber(c)~=0 then incoming_buffer=incoming_buffer..string.char(input.getNumber(c)) col={input.getNumber(10),input.getNumber(11),input.getNumber(12)} end end if not recv and#incoming_buffer>0 then table.insert(messages,incoming_buffer) incoming_buffer="" table.insert(cols,col) end for c=5,7 do if#outgoing_buffer>0 then output.setNumber(c,string.byte(string.sub(outgoing_buffer,1,1))) outgoing_buffer=string.sub(outgoing_buffer,2,#outgoing_buffer)else output.setNumber(c,0) if c~=5 then send=false end end end if input.getBool(3)and not recv then send=true outgoing_buffer=my_m my_m="" end if send then output.setNumber(1,input.getNumber(9))else output.setNumber(1,-1) end for c=2,4 do output.setNumber(c,input.getNumber(14+c)) end output.setBool(32,recv) end
function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight() line=0 if w>64 then messages[1]="----Start of Chat Log----" else messages[1]="Chat Start" end hl=false for d,e in pairs(messages)do screen.setColor(cols[d][1],cols[d][2],cols[d][3]) chars=0 for f,g in pairs(split("> " ..e,"\n" ))do if hl then screen.setColor(32,32,32) screen.drawRectF(0,line*(font_h+1)-scroll-1,w,font_h+1) screen.setColor(cols[d][1],cols[d][2],cols[d][3]) end for i,c in pairs(split(g," " ))do if chars+#c>(w-8)/(font_w+1)then line=line+1 chars=2 if hl then screen.setColor(32,32,32) screen.drawRectF(0,line*(font_h+1)-scroll-1,w,font_h+1) screen.setColor(cols[d][1],cols[d][2],cols[d][3]) end end screen.drawText(4+chars*(font_w+1),line*(font_h+1)-scroll,c) chars=chars+#c+1 end line=line+1 chars=2 end hl=not hl end screen.setColor(64,64,64) screen.drawRectF(w-9,0,7,5) screen.drawRectF(w-9,h-font_h*3-10,7,5) screen.setColor(255,255,255) screen.drawTriangle(w-4,3,w-6,1,w-8,3) screen.drawLine(w-6,1,w-6,3) screen.drawTriangle(w-4,h-(font_h*3+1)-8,w-6,h-(font_h*3+1)-6,w-8,h-(font_h*3+1)-8) screen.drawLine(w-6,h-(font_h*3+1)-6,w-6,h-(font_h*3+1)-8) screen.drawLine(0,h-((font_h+1)*3+2),w,h-((font_h+1)*3+2)) screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawRectF(0,h-(font_h+1)*3-1,w,h-(font_h+1)*3+1) chars=0 line=0 screen.setColor(255,255,255) for f,g in pairs(split(my_m,"\n" ))do chars=0 spaces={} for i,c in pairs(split(g," " ))do if chars+#c>(w-8)/(font_w+1)then line=line+1 chars=0 end screen.drawText(4+chars*(font_w+1),h-(font_h+1)*3+line*(font_h+1),c) chars=chars+#c+1 end line=line+1 end if line==0 then line=1 end if t%60<30 then screen.drawLine(chars*(font_w+1),h-(font_h+1)*3+line*(font_h+1)-font_h-1,chars*(font_w+1),h-(font_h+1)*3+line*(font_h+1)-1) end end

lines = {"1234567890-=<", "qwertyuiop[]", "asdfghjkl;'#", "\\zxcvbnm,./"} lines_shift = {"!\".$%^&*()_+<", "QWERTYUIOP{}", "ASDFGHJKL:@~", "|ZXCVBNM<>?"} colours = {{255, 0, 0}, {0, 255, 0}, {0, 0, 255}, {255, 255, 0}, {255, 0, 255}, {0, 255, 255}, {255, 255, 255}} ci = 1 colour = {255, 0, 0} font_h = 5 font_w = 4 was_pressed = false shift = false
function onTick() pressed = input.getBool(1) w = input.getNumber(1) h = input.getNumber(2) x = input.getNumber(3) y = input.getNumber(4) output.setBool(1, false)
if pressed and not(was_pressed) then xc = (x) // (font_w+1) + 1 yc = ((y-(h-(font_h+1)*5))+2) // (font_h+1) + 1 if shift then line = lines_shift[yc] else line = lines[yc] end
if xc == 13 and yc == 1 then-- Backspace output.setNumber(1, 8) elseif x < ((font_w+1)*4)+2 and y > h-(font_h+1) then shift = not shift elseif x > 3+(font_w*5) and y > h-(font_h+1) and x < 3+(font_w*5)+((font_w+1)*4)-1 then output.setNumber(1, string.byte(" ")) elseif x > 3+(font_w*5)+((font_w+1)*4)-1 and y > h-(font_h+1) then if shift then output.setNumber(1, string.byte("\n")) else output.setBool(1, true) end else if line ~= nil then char = string.sub(line, xc, xc) if char ~= "" then output.setNumber(1, string.byte(char)) end end end else output.setNumber(1, 0) end if x > (w-(font_w))-1 and y > h-(((font_h+1)*2)+3) and y < h-((font_h+1)+2) and pressed and not(was_pressed) then ci = ci + 1 if ci > #colours then ci = 1 end end was_pressed = pressed colour = colours[ci] output.setNumber(2, colour[1]) output.setNumber(3, colour[2]) output.setNumber(4, colour[3]) end
function onDraw() h = screen.getHeight() l = h-(font_h+1)*5 if shift then ln = lines_shift else ln = lines end for j, line in pairs(ln) do ch = 0 for i = 1, #line do screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(ch, l, font_w, font_h) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) c = string.sub(line, i, i) screen.drawText(ch, l, c) ch = ch + font_w + 1 end l = l + font_h + 1 end screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, h-(font_h+1), ((font_w+1)*4)+2, font_h) screen.drawRectF(3+(font_w*5), h-(font_h+1), ((font_w+1)*4)-1, font_h) screen.drawRectF(3+(font_w*10), h-(font_h+1), ((font_w+1)*4)+3, font_h)
screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawText(3, h-(font_h+1), "shft") screen.drawText(3+(font_w*5), h-(font_h+1), "____") if shift then screen.drawText(4+(font_w*10), h-(font_h+1), "ret") else screen.drawText(4+(font_w*10), h-(font_h+1), "send") end screen.drawLine((font_w + 1)*(#lines[1]-1), h-(font_h+1)*4.6, (font_w + 1)*#lines[1], h-(font_h+1)*4.6)
screen.setColor(colour[1], colour[2], colour[3]) screen.drawRectF(w-(font_w), h-((font_h+1)*2), font_w+1, font_h)
end
